00:08:19.310 --> 00:08:21.489
If we go back 50
years in our history,

00:08:21.489 --> 00:08:24.030
the people that used to exercise
in this country on a regular

00:08:24.030 --> 00:08:30.420
basis seemed healthier and more
fit than the people who didn't.

00:08:30.420 --> 00:08:31.770
That's not the same anymore.

00:08:31.770 --> 00:08:34.370
The people who exercise
regularly right now

00:08:34.370 --> 00:08:37.880
in our culture are more fit than
people that don't, but they're

00:08:37.880 --> 00:08:39.530
not more healthy.

00:08:39.530 --> 00:08:42.120
They actually have more
musculoskeletal issues

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:44.730
than people who
choose not to express

00:08:44.730 --> 00:08:46.940
their self physically
three times a week

00:08:46.940 --> 00:08:49.030
in a package of exercise.

00:08:49.030 --> 00:08:53.550
Exercise is a friggin'
risk factor now for health,

00:08:53.550 --> 00:08:54.940
not fitness.

00:08:54.940 --> 00:08:57.716
Exercise will allow you to do
more of what you want to do.

00:08:57.716 --> 00:08:59.840
Just keep doing more of it
and you'll do more of it

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:01.020
until you blow up.

00:09:01.020 --> 00:09:04.300
