making you healthier

00:09:04.300 --> 00:09:07.080
when 80% of the
runners in a given year

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:09.930
will not be able to run.

00:09:09.930 --> 00:09:11.887
And they want to
run, but they can't.

00:09:11.887 --> 00:09:15.790
They created a health
issue trying to be fit.

00:09:15.790 --> 00:09:18.190
Don't put your fitness on
a movement dysfunction,

00:09:18.190 --> 00:09:21.070
